        private void decideEquation(java.lang.String variable1,
                            java.lang.String operation1,
                            java.lang.String variable2,
                            java.lang.String operation2,
                            java.lang.String variable3,
                            double result)
        decides the value for the equation, valueEquation, and result attributes
        Parameters:
        variable1 - the first variable in the equation
        operation1 - the first operation character in the equation evaluating the first and second variable
        variable2 - the second variable in the equation
        operation2 - the second operation character in the equation evaluating the second and third variable
        variable3 - the third variable in the equation
        result - the solution to the equation
